claims.text:
A method for assembling a portable computing device with an integrated keyboard and display, comprising:
providing a compact form factor chassis for easy transportation;
integrating a battery power source for untethered use within the chassis;
incorporating various input/output ports for connectivity within the chassis; and
assembling the integrated keyboard and display within the compact form factor chassis to form the portable computing device.

